document_data.name: Fangs of Set
document_data.mainbody: '''The Fangs of Set''' was an organization that tried to rule [[Mulhorand]] from the shadows, leading the nation along a path of [[Set]]'s design.<ref>
document_data.Members: They were an adventuring party gathered in [[1357 DR]] by [[Seti]], the living [[incarnation]] of [[Set]]. It was composed of four members, [[Hodkamset]], [[Nekiset]], [[Hamsetis]] and [[Suliyar]], each one commanded a variable numbers of minions.
